	<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en">Howard Scott</h1>
	
	<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
		<div id="siteSub" class="noprint">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</div>
		<div id="contentSub"></div>
		
		
		<div id="jump-to-nav"></div>
		<a class="mw-jump-link" href="#mw-head">Jump to navigation</a>
		<a class="mw-jump-link" href="#p-search">Jump to search</a>
		<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">For other people named Howard Scott, see <a href="/wiki/Howard_Scott_(disambiguation)" class="mw-disambig" title="Howard Scott (disambiguation)">Howard Scott (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
<div class="thumb tright"><div class="thumbinner" style="width:222px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Howard_Scott_at_a_Technocracy_Section_house.jpg" class="image"><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/7/7f/Howard_Scott_at_a_Technocracy_Section_house.jpg/220px-Howard_Scott_at_a_Technocracy_Section_house.jpg" decoding="async" width="220" height="312" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/7/7f/Howard_Scott_at_a_Technocracy_Section_house.jpg/330px-Howard_Scott_at_a_Technocracy_Section_house.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/7/7f/Howard_Scott_at_a_Technocracy_Section_house.jpg/440px-Howard_Scott_at_a_Technocracy_Section_house.jpg 2x" data-file-width="564" data-file-height="800" /></a>  <div class="thumbcaption"><div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Howard_Scott_at_a_Technocracy_Section_house.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"></a></div>Howard Scott in front of Technocracy Inc. Section house RD-11833-2 SHQ in 1942.</div></div></div>
<p><b>Howard Scott</b> (April 1, 1890 – January 1, 1970) was an American engineer and founder of the <a href="/wiki/Technocracy_movement" title="Technocracy movement">Technocracy movement</a>. He formed the <a href="/wiki/Technical_Alliance" title="Technical Alliance">Technical Alliance</a> and <a href="/wiki/Technocracy_Incorporated" class="mw-redirect" title="Technocracy Incorporated">Technocracy Incorporated</a>.<sup id="cite_ref-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-1">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>
</p>
<div id="toc" class="toc" role="navigation" aria-labelledby="mw-toc-heading"><input type="checkbox" role="button" id="toctogglecheckbox" class="toctogglecheckbox" style="display:none" /><div class="toctitle" lang="en" dir="ltr"><h2 id="mw-toc-heading">Contents</h2><span class="toctogglespan"><label class="toctogglelabel" for="toctogglecheckbox"></label></span></div>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-1"><a href="#Early_life"><span class="tocnumber">1</span> <span class="toctext">Early life</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-2"><a href="#Technocracy"><span class="tocnumber">2</span> <span class="toctext">Technocracy</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-3"><a href="#Genesis_of_the_technocratic_movement"><span class="tocnumber">3</span> <span class="toctext">Genesis of the technocratic movement</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-4"><a href="#Radical_reform"><span class="tocnumber">4</span> <span class="toctext">Radical reform</span></a></li>
